title.label: Great game, but price is unreasonable

content.label:
I loved Labyrinth, and the new Labyrinth 2 is brilliant.
The new elements that it provides really enhance the play, and the GUI and 'feel' of the game is superb.

I'd love to buy it, ... but $5 is entirely unreasonable.

If you want people to line up to get this game, you're going to have to rethink your pricing strategy to bring it inline with the rest of the games on iTunes.
